assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Ajial Real Estate Entertainment Company K.S.C.P. operates as a real estate company in Kuwait. The company operates through two segments, Real Estate Investing Activities, and Equities and Other Investing Activities. The Real Estate Investing Activities segment invests and trades in real estate; constructs or develops real estate properties; and offers other related real estate services. The Equities and Other Investing Activities segment participates in financial and real estate funds. The company also purchases, rents, leases, and sells real estate properties; establishes and maintains buildings and real estate projects, including residential complexes; and establishes commercial markets, entertainment centers, touristic facilities, and building accommodations, as well as trades in building materials. Ajial Real Estate Entertainment Company K.S.C.P. was incorporated in 1996 and is headquartered in Kuwait City, Kuwait.
